<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: transparent; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; overflow: hidden; }
        .header-wrapper { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header-banner {
            position: relative; width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f7b40 0%, #159c52 50%, #0a572c 100%);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 15px 5%; box-sizing: border-box; gap: 15px;
        }
        .header-banner::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 150%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%),
                              radial-gradient(circle at 90% -30%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 40%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .text-container { z-index: 1; text-align: right; color: #ffffff; flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .text-container h1 { font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; margin: 0; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 700; text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); line-height: 1.2; }
        .text-container p { margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 2.5vw, 1.3rem); letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700; color: #d1f2df; text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .logo-container img { height: clamp(60px, 15vw, 110px); width: clamp(60px, 15vw, 110px); object-fit: contain; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 50%; padding: 6px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border: 3px solid #b3e6c9; }
        .ticker-container { width: 100%; background-color: #084c25; padding: 8px 0; overflow: hidden; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        .ticker-text { display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; color: #d1f2df; font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; padding-left: 100%; animation: scroll 20s linear infinite; }
        @keyframes scroll { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(-100%); } }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .header-banner { padding: 10px 15px; } .text-container h1 { line-height: 1.1; } .text-container p { font-size: 0.9rem; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-wrapper">
        <div class="header-banner">
            <div class="text-container">
                <h1>المندوبية الإندونيسية</h1>
                <p>PPMI MADINAH</p>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1RIT1Gm7ICdsZruNqS0EpEK2J3PIYws5E" alt="Logo" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/110/ffffff/0f7b40?text=Logo'">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ticker-container" dir="ltr">
            <div class="ticker-text">
                أهلاً بكم في الموقع المصغر الداخلي للمندوبية الإندونيسية • Selamat datang di microsite internal PPMI Madinah •
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Pengaturan dasar agar pas di Google Sites */
        body { 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 10px; 
            background-color: transparent; 
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; 
        }

        .humas-section {
            background: #ffffff; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-top: 5px solid #159c52; 
            text-align: center;
            position: relative; 
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Dekorasi latar belakang */
        .humas-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#159c52 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 25px 25px;
            opacity: 0.03;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .humas-header h2 { 
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; 
            color: #0a572c; 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 1.8rem; 
        }

        .humas-header h3 { 
            color: #159c52; 
            margin: 5px 0 15px 0; 
            font-size: 1.05rem; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .humas-content p { 
            color: #555; 
            font-size: 0.9rem; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* Wadah tombol yang sejajar */
        .humas-links { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            gap: 10px; 
            flex-wrap: wrap; 
            direction: ltr; /* Tombol mengalir dari kiri ke kanan */
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .humas-btn {
            padding: 10px 18px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            background: #f0fdf4;
            color: #0f7b40; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-size: 0.85rem; 
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid #bceacb; 
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            gap: 8px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            max-width: 200px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* Tombol aksi utama dengan sedikit penekanan warna */
        .humas-btn.primary {
            background: #159c52;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: #159c52;
        }

        .humas-btn:hover { 
            background: #159c52; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            transform: translateY(-3px); 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(21, 156, 82, 0.2);
            border-color: #159c52;
        }

        .humas-btn.primary:hover {
            background: #0a572c;
            border-color: #0a572c;
        }

        /* Optimalisasi layar HP */
        @media (max-width: 600px) { 
            .humas-header h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; } 
            .humas-header h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; }
            .humas-links { gap: 8px; }
            .humas-btn { 
                flex-basis: calc(50% - 8px); 
                font-size: 0.8rem; 
                padding: 10px 12px;
                max-width: 100%;
            } 
        }

        @media (max-width: 400px) {
            .humas-btn {
                flex-basis: 100%; /* Menjadi satu baris per tombol di layar sangat kecil */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="humas-section">
        <div class="humas-header">
            <h2>قسم العلاقات العامة</h2>
            <h3>DIVISI HUBUNGAN MASYARAKAT</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="humas-content">
            <p>Pusat informasi, komunikasi, dan pelayanan aspirasi bagi seluruh pelajar dan mahasiswa Indonesia di Madinah.</p>
            
            <div class="humas-links">
                <!-- Tombol Pendataan & Statistik (Sejajar) -->
                <a href="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbz3Rl7cHZPijFcAM-zSmO3J624j_Q7LLb-eUgkwN1TkwPBteNPqIhGGq72QqzKP97dv/exec" target="_blank" class="humas-btn primary">📝 Pendataan KJRI 2026</a>
                <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/ppmi-madinah/statistik" target="_blank" class="humas-btn primary">📊 Statistik</a>
                
                <!-- Tombol Media Sosial & Informasi -->
                <a href="https://instagram.com/ppmimadinah" target="_blank" class="humas-btn">📸 Instagram</a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/6281313777542" target="_blank" class="humas-btn">💬 Informasi</a>
                <a href="#" target="_blank" class="humas-btn">🌐 Microsite</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
